  "title": "Glowing Ores Universal - Emissive Ores for ALL Mods",
  "description": "This Mod will glow the ores and some Minecraft blocks BUT also the MODS ORES that we will add in each update!",
  "body": "![what is this?](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/77fdc6d4167014720ffd91862297a576ab78b6a1.png)\nThis MOD will glow the ores and some Minecraft blocks BUT also the various mods that we will add in each update!\n\n![Compatibility](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f51835ea71f75f6a92c77590768c696d0de6d23d.png)\nThis Mod is Compatible with:\n\n\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/924/13/vanilla_blocks.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1069907/description_a6793505-09a1-4fdf-8d30-e64a7eda153c.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1069907/description_2290e5d2-395e-448e-98ba-8be7051632ff.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"//media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1069907/description_b979dab2-f153-42c2-ad01-6d28b06980c4.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_878584d7-73fb-4c6f-966d-f071d1ad83c6.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_93e548f9-5ebc-458f-9f00-e7b5ccc08545.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_9b69ed0e-de00-4cd5-955a-ed579f75acd8.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1069907/description_abd926db-50d0-4de8-a3ae-e52311c9d33a.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_85444cf9-c4a9-4e8d-be42-f3b961ce644a.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/924/252/dungeons_plus_blocks.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1069907/description_d47bf811-31d8-458a-a57f-9a61342a38f7.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_1c5f2c25-eb7f-4e24-87cd-0420ef76c014.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1069907/description_d47bf811-31d8-458a-a57f-9a61342a38f7.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_a1aff1a8-f297-4f82-ac27-c932dacfecd8.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_ed194378-2287-4085-8e1c-a902f32b42f4.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_2a87dc43-75bd-4043-91c9-c4372892bf7d.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_183fe7dc-137a-4499-b4e8-f9310a941d0a.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_85018b92-d7c0-4bc2-bf06-ffd52b77cfb2.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_f2f1f428-8565-461e-a401-76cfb9dcaf04.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1249404/description_0fd15ad6-fbd8-46af-ac8a-c8b8acb11d82.gif\" width=\"188\" height=\"181\"/>\n\nSomething that stands out about our Mod above the others is that we have maximum Compatibility with **MANY MODS**, so the Ores of your **Favorite Mods** will also have that **Glow effect**! \n\n![Faq](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ac8ba9c8209a2c55f8d90d55c4acb2cec36f6d59.png)\n## *How can I see the Glow Ores if I don't use Optifine?*\nIf you are using Embeddium, you must download these 2 mods:  \n[MoreMcmeta Emissive Textures (Forge)](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/moremcmeta-emissive-forge)    |    [MoreMcmeta (Forge)](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/moremcmeta)\n\n![Support](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3f862540c623b931440765cd3f437eb7f0ad9513.png)\nIf you like to support us, you can Join our  <span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/N6TsrGvzvZ\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord</a></span> or Support us monetarily on our <span style=\"color: #3598db;\">&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #3598db;\" href=\"https://www.patreon.com/RenovatedStudios\" rel=\"nofollow\">Patreon</a></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/N6TsrGvzvZ\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1017834/description_f9406618-0e4f-4d0a-92da-5376ba49b9e8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"354\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/RenovatedStudios\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1017834/description_fb2b698d-66ca-4888-a0c3-460d706e5304.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"354\" height=\"82\"></a></span>",
